import React from 'react';
import { TextField, Button } from '@material-ui/core';
import { FormDialog, QuestionDialog } from '../Shared/Dialog';

export function AddUserDialog(props) { 
    const [selected, setSelected] = React.useState(null)  
    const [login, setLogin] = React.useState(null)
    const [password, setPassword] = React.useState(null)

    return (
    <FormDialog isOpen={props.isOpen} onClose={props.onClose} title={props.title}>
      <TextField
      autoFocus
      required
      margin="dense"
      id="login"
      label="Login"
      type="text"
      fullWidth
      onChange={(event) => {setLogin(event.target.value)}}
      />

      <TextField
      autoFocus
      required
      margin="dense"
      id="password"
      label="Password"
      type="password"
      fullWidth
      onChange={(event) => {setPassword(event.target.value)}}
      />

      <select name="Type">
      <option value="Empty" selected>Empty</option>
      {props.types.map(type => <option value={type} onSelect={() => {setSelected(type)}}>{type}</option>)}
      </select>
    </FormDialog>)
}

export const EditUserDialog = (props) =>
    <FormDialog isOpen={props.isOpen} onClose={props.onClose} title={props.title}>
      <TextField
            autoFocus
            required
            margin="dense"
            id="login"
            label="Login"
            type="text"
            fullWidth
          />

        <TextField
            autoFocus
            margin="dense"
            id="password"
            label="Password"
            type="password"
            fullWidth
          />

        <TextField
            autoFocus
            margin="dense"
            id="type"
            label="Type"
            type="password"
            fullWidth
          />
    </FormDialog>

export const DeleteUserDialog = (props) =>
    <QuestionDialog isOpen={props.isOpen} title={props.title}>
      <Button onClick={() => {props.onClose('cancel')}} color="primary">
        Cancel 
      </Button>
      <Button onClick={() => {props.onClose('delete')}} color="primary">
        Delete 
      </Button>
    </QuestionDialog>
